<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Fibers on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/fibers/</link><description>Recent content in Fibers on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 May 2021 20:34:08 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/fibers/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>There is an issue with node-fibers</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2021/05/12/m1%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91taro%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 May 2021 20:34:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2021/05/12/m1%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91taro%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="macbook-m1和taro"&gt;&lt;code&gt;MacBook M1&lt;/code&gt;和&lt;code&gt;taro&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在MacBook M1上运行&lt;code&gt;taro&lt;/code&gt;项目&lt;code&gt;yarn dev:h5&lt;/code&gt;的时候会报下面的错误：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;## There is an issue with `node-fibers` ##
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;`/node_modules/fibers/bin/darwin-arm64-88/fibers.node` is missing.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Try running this to fix the issue: .nvm/versions/node/v15.5.0/bin/node /node_modules/fibers/build
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Error: Cannot find module &amp;#39;node_modules/fibers/bin/darwin-arm64-88/fibers&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;找了很久没找到解决方案，知道找个一个类似的问题：https://www.jianshu.com/p/145015d721a5&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>